        <h2 class="section-description">Contributing for sustainability of NGO Monte Azul through strategic design.</h2>

        <h3>CONTEXT</h3>
        <p>The Monte Azul Community Association is a non-governmental organization that operates primarily for the integral development of the human being, through projects and actions in education, food, health, environment and culture. Currently, a decrease of resources is concerned the NGO, and our challenge is to contribute to the sustainability of Monte Azul through strategic design.</p>

