        <h3>RESEARCH AND WORKSHOP</h3>
        <p>Our research was focused in understanding the role of philosophy, how do people understand anthroposophy as a human change experiment? How to make the Monte Azul speech more flexible and more comprehensive understanding? And how to structure thinking actions the future of Monte Azul?</p>

